#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectortable.rst:858
msgid "Default: True"
msgstr "Standard: Sann"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectortable.rst:87
msgid ""
"When a ``sort expression`` is set, use this option to control the order in "
